Add Tableau View to a Dashboard

Compare and review Tableau and CRM Analytics data side by side in a CRM Analytics dashboard. Embed a published Tableau Cloud or Tableau Server view in a CRM Analytics dashboard to analyze your data without switching between two accounts.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

To add the Tableau view, drop a component widget onto the dashboard and click Component.
In the Select Component window, select the Tableau view from the Tableau Dashboard Components list.
Save your dashboard and then preview it.
title: Embedding Tableau Views in CRM Analytics
